headline: 1 No-Brainer Stock-Split Stock to Buy Before the End of the Year, and 1 That Investors Would Be Wise to Avoid
summary: Among Netflix, O'Reilly Automotive, Interactive Brokers, Fastenal, and Lucid Group, there's a company with undeniable tailwinds in its sails, as well as another that appears headed for a breakdown.
